  @EC-6 @SM-1105
  Scenario: API error is handled gracefully when network drops during cascade template save
    When I click the "Project Admin" sidebar parent menu
    And I click the "Cascade Templates" sidebar menu item
    Then I should see the page title "Cascade Templates"
    When the network connection is interrupted
    And I click the "Save" button
    Then I should see an error message indicating the save failed
    And no template data should be lost or corrupted
    When the network connection is restored
    And I click the "Save" button
    Then the template should be saved successfully

